Package com.pandora.config.species.abstractions

Interface SpecieConfiguration

All Superinterfaces:
VariableConfiguration
All Known Subinterfaces:
Carbon
All Known Implementing Classes:
AqueousSpecie, DIC, DOC, SedimentarySpecie, Specie
public interface SpecieConfiguration extends VariableConfiguration
The SpecieConfiguration interface extends the VariableConfiguration interface and provides an additional method for retrieving the molar mass of the biogeochemical species. The molar mass represents the mass of one mole of the species and is a crucial parameter for various biogeochemical calculations.
Version:
0.0.1
Author:
Wim Joost van Hoek
